Maintainer:          Gero Kriependorf <gero-dev@physra.net>
Stability:           Testing
Category:            Logging
Build-type:          Simple
Cabal-version:       >=1.6
Library
  Exposed-modules:     System.Log.SessionLogger
  Hs-Source-Dirs:      src
  Build-depends:       base==4.*, mtl==1.1.1.*, time==1.*, hslogger==1.*,
                       directory==1.*, filepath==1.*, old-locale==1.0.*,
                       random==1.0.*
